      <title>欧洲央行表示银行认为欧元区信贷需求触底反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/ecb-says-banks-see-euro-zone-credit-demand-bottoming-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行表示，由于利率上升和经济陷入困境，欧元区信贷需求在经历一年多的下降后可能正在触底反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/ecb-says-banks-see-euro-zone-credit-demand-bottoming-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
